HEADWORD: Monophyllous
<hw>Mo*noph"yl*lous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>mono`fyllos</grk>; <grk>mo`nos</grk> alone + <grk>fy`llon</grk>
